title: Extra Tickets for EULCS Finals in Hamburg
body:
I have two extra tickets for the EULCS final in Hamburg later today!

Seats are I3 Row 3 Seat 7 & 8. So really good and directly in front of the casters. 

Looking for 30 Euro each but prices are negotiable. 

Proof:
http://i.imgur.com/oJnpFA2.jpg
